race.comment: HARDLY FORTUNATE (4) resumed and accounted for a Maiden field over 1200m at this track. She's further improved, and Heywood sticks in the saddle. She has plenty of upside and can take the next step for the Olive yard. LIAMENA AVENUE (8) deserved his Maiden win here when he led and then disappointed in a CL1 at Wyong (vet cleared). Better suited today, and fourth up will get every chance to bounce. ANTHRACIA (7) has won 4x at home and was quickly back on track, narrowly beaten here in a 66. Carries 3kg more, but she will race forward and has each-way claims. ONYA LIONAL (3) would be a contender at best and can show more third-up in easier company. An in-form jockey is engaged.
